PROBLEM     : knp-2
DESCRIPTION : Knapsack problem with d=2 items of increasing weights w = [1,2,...,d] and maximum capacity W=d. The cost vector encodes the items value as c = [c_{1},c_{2},...,c_{d}] where c_{i}=value(i).
ORACLE      : LDTREE (MINIMUM-DEPTH PROVEN)

POINTS 3 2
0 [0,0]
1 [1,0]
2 [0,1]

SPLITS 3 2
0 [1,0]
1 [0,1]
2 [1,-1]

LDTREE 3 1 2
0 NODE 2 {LT:1,GT:2}
1 LEAF {2}
2 LEAF {1}
